MessageForDeleted.BH.Engine.Spatial.Query.Area(BH.oM.Dimen: Querying the area of a 0 diemnsional is not possible. The method was added in error and should not have been available. Area methods are suitable for 2D objects and above.
Area of an IElement1D cannot be queried because IElement1D has only 1 dimension, i.e. should not be represented as a region even if closed. Method has been removed to avoid confusion.
